{"tid":1294870,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今工上班衣著：黑衫廿罩 著黑衫戴口罩不是罪","createTime":"2019-07-08T00:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T01:49:06.000Z","uid":3206,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"973c55e3eded3edb574673d3322fa70a08dbad73","tid":1294870,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"你老母啲狗亂尻咁咬<br />\n你估佢哋查你身份證之餘唔撚驚你咩？<br />\n明知去開遊行嘅都係憎警察<br />\n你估佢哋面對被周街敵視會冇心理壓力咩？唔撚怯咩？<br />\n我就同你製造心理壓力<br />\n經過巡警記得用你雙眼望實佢<br />\n佢哋查你你唔需要講嘢，配合調查之餘依然望實佢<br />\n直頭佢查完離開，你嘅眼神要追蹤住佢嘅身影直至消失<br />\n<br />\n武力鬥不過，就喺其他方面製造佢哋嘅心理壓力<br />\n唔好同我講巡警輔警無辜<br />\n佢哋冇一個係無辜<br />\n<br />\n自問無辜嘅話 你好好多謝吓自己啲同事啦  仆街狗"},{"pid":"bd10ad9d5a175ab6d107ded142a6c602ddc58371","tid":1294870,"uid":3206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7m5zG91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7m5zG91.png&h=88739a42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5b29d52c793bfb4455be5f9bd70aee1ca17a3d0","tid":1294870,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:03:27.000Z","msg":"屌老尾我嬲到打撚錯晒個標題原來"},{"pid":"63ed678c23020b90287c550aaeef684362707144","tid":1294870,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"網民定性7月7日警方行動為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察暴動</span></span>["},{"pid":"cf08665527e85ba99db428c5b175ee8752327ae4","tid":1294870,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63ed678c23020b90287c550aaeef684362707144","tid":1294870,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"網民定性7月7日警方行動為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察暴動</span></span>["},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"香港警察<br />\n知法犯法"},{"pid":"9c235fbeb9fed04d88aea90243de42eef130274c","tid":1294870,"uid":3206,"like":0